    <title>webpack的使用</title>
    <link href="https://matisha001.github.io/2015/03/19/webpack/"/>
    <id>https://matisha001.github.io/2015/03/19/webpack/</id>
    <published>2015-03-18T16:34:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-10-06T07:37:59.414Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装webpack"><a href="#安装webpack" class="headerlink" title="安装webpack"></a>安装webpack</h2><blockquote><p>npm i webpack -g</p><p>webpack –help</p></blockquote><h2 id="使用webpack创建项目"><a href="#使用webpack创建项目" class="headerlink" title="使用webpack创建项目"></a>使用webpack创建项目</h2><blockquote><p>npm init </p><p>npm i webpack</p><p>webpack enter.js  bundle.js</p></blockquote><p> 打包生成的bundle.js包含webpack本身需要的一些东西。</p> <a id="more"></a><h3 id="模块依赖"><a href="#模块依赖" class="headerlink" title="模块依赖"></a>模块依赖</h3><blockquote><p>main.js<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; var test=require(&apos;./test&apos;);</div><div class="line">&gt; console.log(test)</div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>test.js<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; module.exports=&quot;matisha001&quot;</div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><h3 id="loader转换器"><a href="#loader转换器" class="headerlink" title="loader转换器"></a>loader转换器</h3><p> loader转换器是将资源从一种形式转化为另一种形式，最总转化为js。</p><blockquote><p>常见的转换器<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; css-loader、style-loader等</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">'style!css!./style.css'</span>);</div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><h3 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h3><blockquote><p>默认的配置文件为webpack.config.js</p><p>输入 webpack命令 </p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">module.exports = &#123;</div><div class="line">  entry:&apos;./entry.js&apos;,//入口文件</div><div class="line">  output:&#123;//生成文件</div><div class="line">    path:__dirname,</div><div class="line">    filename:&apos;bundle.js&apos;</div><div class="line">  &#125;,</div><div class="line">  devtool:&apos;source-map&apos;,//生成source-map文件</div><div class="line">  module:&#123; //要使用的模块</div><div class="line">    loaders:[</div><div class="line">      &#123;test:/\.css$/,loader:&apos;style!css&apos;&#125;</div><div class="line">    ]</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="调试代码-source-map"><a href="#调试代码-source-map" class="headerlink" title="调试代码 source-map"></a>调试代码 source-map</h3><blockquote><p>生成source-map文件</p><p>webpack –devtool source-map</p><p>test.js<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">debugger</span>;  <span class="comment">//代码打断点</span></div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="built_in">module</span>.exports=<span class="string">"matisha001"</span></div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;安装webpack&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#安装webpack&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;安装webpack&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;安装webpack&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;npm i webpack -g&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;webpack –help&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;使用webpack创建项目&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#使用webpack创建项目&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;使用webpack创建项目&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;使用webpack创建项目&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;npm init &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;npm i webpack&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;webpack enter.js  bundle.js&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt; 打包生成的bundle.js包含webpack本身需要的一些东西。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
